{"tid":54876,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港樓根本係垃圾。】 193 呎點住3個人？設計師拆局大揭秘","createTime":"2016-12-26T02:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T04:59:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ed443cf840b2f843ed6c8eba2a74b69fd78b84b","tid":54876,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T02:16:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【香港樓根本係垃圾。】<br />\n193 呎點住3個人？設計師拆局大揭秘</strong></span><br />\n2016年12月25日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161223/large/1482492940_baa5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161223%2Flarge%2F1482492940_baa5.jpg&h=886e8d23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n趟開係咁樣，有條樓梯可供上床。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓價升、面積縮，開放式單位氾濫成災，住戶惟有靠裝修設計及多功能家具改造居住環境。室內設計師Terrence指，善用收納式家具，即使是2016年開則最差、面積狹隘的開放式單位，執正後也可讓一家三口住在一起。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161225/large/1482650506_7d7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161225%2Flarge%2F1482650506_7d7b.jpg&h=5b976081&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n模擬北角尚譽193方呎單位，夫婦二人及一個小孩居住在內。Terrence指單位可以保持原有間隔，大門後方置一組訂造衣櫃，下方則為酒店式雪櫃。旁邊的開放式廚房下方安裝收納式餐檯及餐椅，露台亦可造吧檯作天晴時的用餐區，以盡用每呎空間。<br />\n<br />\n中央區域則由一張組合床佔據，面向廚櫃位置做斜板鞋櫃，部份位置設計成屏風以減少壓迫感。將組合床往窗邊拉趟，方出現往上方床舖的樓梯，床闊四呎，梯級有儲物功能，增加儲物量。床下方的空間置電視機櫃及一張收納式單人床，雙人梳化則置於窗邊。不過，設計公司指上述設計方案暫時未能提供裝備費用預算。<br />\n<br />\n同時，節省空間的多功能家具成為劏房救星。市面上有室內設計及訂造傢俬公司提供多種變形家具，Decor House負責人指，近年該類產品需求有所增加。<br />\n<br />\n 【更新尚譽最新銷情】<br />\n<br />\n北角尚譽由恒地(012)發展，全盤128伙單位全部不足300呎，絕大部份為開放式單位，最細面積低見163方呎，細過小巴。發展商今年9月份推出首批50伙，全數為C及D室單位。樓盤目前售出32伙，平均成交呎價約2.39萬元，本月只售出1伙。<br />\n<br />\n上文提到的A室單位則仍未推售，據售樓說明說顯示，單位交樓時附設數項基本家電，包括Panasonic分體式冷氣機、TGC煤氣爐頭及熱水爐、西門子洗衣乾衣機、抽油煙機、微波爐、嵌入式雪櫃。<br />\n<br />\n短片：<br />\n<a href=\"http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2016/12/24/3238417/20161217_fin_902_final_new_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F3238417%2F20161217_fin_902_final_new_w.mp4&d=xIgoi0qI1Uh9wtwXt3H%2Fzwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=f8de769a\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2016/12/24/3238417/20161217_fin_902_final_new_w.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n原文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20161225/56085325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20161225%2F56085325&d=xIgoi0qI1Uh9wtwXt3H%2Fzwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=23214e36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20161225%2F56085325&h=e8592b23\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20161225/56085325</a>"},{"pid":"51f28bdc1124a12ed7f1107b0a9bf457be6cdec6","tid":54876,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T04:27:39.000Z","msg":"無位擺魚缸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42fcebe16d2dcc4dd475c1da16fbe465947b539","tid":54876,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T04:33:39.000Z","msg":"點解呢啲樓都會有人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7226fc6f7909c870250b76de5ec809502ea6cb5","tid":54876,"uid":57695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T04:38:33.000Z","msg":"頂頭點玩狗仔式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab79a16e07de8f3a551b52e3faddfa722b26d617","tid":54876,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T04:39:53.000Z","msg":"呎價兩萬幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0aff64a7b90331a743313618f22d5bb0d1ab103","tid":54876,"uid":29874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T04:43:01.000Z","msg":"香港人真係有病，193尺跟本唔係比人住，仲要一家三口，如果要住得咁辛苦不食老綜住公屋<img src=\